# --- Documentation Access Rules ---
# Ignore all docs except docs/active/ (authoritative source)
docs/_archive/**
docs/legacy/**
docs/reference/**
docs/user/**
# Ignore all markdown files in docs/ except docs/active/
docs/**/*.md
!docs/active/**/*.md

# --- Never read generated / bulky stuff ---
**/node_modules/**
**/.venv/**
**/dist/**
**/build/**
**/.next/**
**/.expo/**
**/coverage/**
**/*.log
**/*.lock
**/*.zip
**/*.tar
**/*.gz
